<HR><H2>[COLD] Exit announcements (anomaly?)</H2>
<H3>daemon@ATHENA.MIT.EDU (Thu Aug 21 19:13:36 1997
)</H3>
<PRE>
From: "Luther, Clay" &lt;clay@selsius.com&gt;
To: "'coldstuff@cold.org'" &lt;coldstuff@cold.org&gt;
Date: Thu, 21 Aug 1997 18:06:51 -0500

While building in the new core, I noticed that exit announcements occur
at an odd time (IMHO).

For instance, if I am standing in a room and take the north exit, I will
see:

	New Room Name
	New Room Description.
	You take the north exit.

Isn't more logical (from a VR point of view) to see:

	You take the north exit.
	New Room Name
	New Room Description.

???

---
Onegaishimasu.

Clay Luther
clay@selsius.com

Hello, hello!  This is Monkey Wrench calling Bunny Hutch Headquarters...

